SIMPLE: anastigmatic
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anastigmatic
<hw>An*as`tig*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>an-</ets>not + <ets>astigmatic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Optics)</fld>
<def>Not astigmatic; free of astigmatism; -- pertaining to a lens or
lens system, and used especially of a lens system which consists of a
converging lens and a diverging lens of equal and opposite astigmatism
but different focal lengths, and sensibly free from
astigmatism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anastomose</ent>⟦br⟧
